    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package based on the bench hemolysis comparison result (MAE 12.4 %, within the 15 % acceptance band) and the PIV velocity comparison (RMS error 8.1 %). The team noted that the hemolysis bench comparison was generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2024-q3 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2), which is consistent with the solver version used at the time of that validation campaign. The team did not flag the discrepancy between this modelVersion and the UofA currentModelVersion (2026-q1-build-7), treating the older result as still applicable to the current model of record. All assessed credibility factors were reviewed; gaps in six not-assessed factors were acknowledged but deemed acceptable given the positive quantitative comparison outcomes.",
